channel.title: Nyanx 508
channel.description:

item.title: Nyanx 508
item.dc:creator: @Mezzyscape562 Mezzyscape562
item.description:
@Mezzyscape562 wrote:

[quote=“Loveandpower, post:5, topic:519049”]I’m a play <3

Name : Babymaking

Yeah I’m going to be an asshole here…
-> you’re =/= posessive
-> new models and gameframe don’t fit with the old hitmarks and hp bars
-> The flashy colors in the chatbox are ugly
-> No unique content.
Conclusion:
This is the 1 miliionth copy of your average RSPS.
Have a nice day…

You really shouldn’t be at least not without first looking at it. This a VERY clean base from what I have seen from just playing from a players pov.

this was sent in client window

java.io.IOException: fds at Class52.method541(Class52.java:50) at Class118.method1730(Class118.java:28) at Class68_Sub13_Sub19.method795(Class68_Sub13_Sub19.java:178) at client.method38(client.java:642) at client.method33(client.java:786) at Applet_Sub1.method30(Applet_Sub1.java:485) at Applet_Sub1.run(Applet_Sub1.java:156) at java.lang.Thread.run(Unknown Source)

Edit #2: Barrows shop crashes/kicks you

Edit #3: Dragon ax is 5 gp xD…

Edit #4: You need to make it so it writes to a file and SAVES even before you log back out. Reason: Well … I didn’t log out and I lost my starter and can’t get another. So I lost all of my hard work so far * cough *

Edit #5: Your player clipping/object clipping could use some work I can walk through certain walls(and then it like does a moonwalk pattern sort of cool xD )

Edit #6: Dialoguehandling could use a good rewriting. If you go to home teleport and teleport talk to a legend guild guy you will see what I mean

And what is up with the 30 minute timer for home teleport? This ins’t RS get rid of it !

Edit #7: ::manual does not work but romeo tells me to view the rules ( which seems sort of redundant if you think about the quest )

Edit #8: Not a bug but I love that goth leprechaun! … mind giving npc id? Or is it custom?

Edit :#9: Did 508 have G.E. ? I didn’t realize this I thought that was like 540-562 ish ?

Edit #10: when you talk to the grand exchange tutor he changes dialogue in mid sentence

Edit #11: Should make it so it saves your “running” status at logout. This way if you was running before you auto run next time.

Edit #12: why are there gnome terrorbirds in lumbridge ? xD ( by cows )

EDIT #13: I’m sorry but I can’t do this any longer until you get a vps or something…constant dc’s irritate the crap out of me.[/quote]
Alright thanks for the feedback i think you lost ur starter because of auto restarter and highscores on crappy vps i will be getting a much better vps and make sure char files will save more often

Read full topic
